dc_description_s: These data layers represent recreation information for Pepin County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase NPepin_Recreation_2018.gdbN. This feature dataset includes nineteen recreation feature classes. [U.S. Water Bodies represents the major lakes, reservoirs, large rivers, lagoons, and estuaries in the United States. U.S. Counties represents the counties of the United States in the 50 states, the District of Columbia, and Puerto Rico.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
